# Canonical author identities for `git log` / `git shortlog`.
#
# Format: Canonical Name <canonical-email> <commit-email>
# See: https://git-scm.com/docs/gitmailmap
#
# Maps personal/legacy emails to the GitHub noreply alias so the public
# git history doesn't expose personal inboxes.

